SUBENT        C3092003   20251211   20260312   20260312       C253
BIB                  4         12
REACTION   (20-CA-40(P,G)21-SC-41,PAR,SGV)
MISC-COL   (MISC1) Low reaction rate
           (MISC2) High reaction rate
ANALYSIS   The total thermonuclear reaction rate of the
           40Ca(p,gamma)41Sc reaction was calculated by summing
           both nonresonant and resonant contributions,
           NA(sigmav)total = NA(sigmav)NR + NA(sigmav) R, where
           NA(sigmav)NR is the nonresonant contribution and
           NA(sigmav) R is the resonant contribution.
